title: (Tues Early Bird) What Is Bobby Filming With Jimmie Allen? + Did Lunchbox Give A Speech At His Cousins Wedding? + Mailbag: Brother-In-Law Fight
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) What Is Bobby Filming With Jimmie Allen? + Did Lunchbox Give A Speech At His Cousins Wedding? + Mailbag: Brother-In-Law Fight
description:
Bobby shares that he is filming something with Jimmie Allen tonight that will also involve Kevin Hart! Find out what it is and why he's super excited for it. Plus, we hear from Lunchbox's cousin about whether she wants him to give a speech at her wedding or not. Mailbag: A listener gave us an update from a mailbag they sent in a few weeks ago about how his brother-in-law wanted to fight him, but he didn't want to... we finally find out what happened!
